@startuml
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title Class Diagram - Multi-Matical Supporter system

class MainMenu {
  - root: tkinter.Tk
  - top_frame: tkinter.Frame
  - button_frame: tkinter.Frame
  + set_dynamic_background(root_window, image_path)
  + start_app()
}

class calculator {
  + {static} open_calculator()
}

class converter {
  + {static} open_converter()
}

class graph {
  + {static} open_graph()
}

class graph_3D {
  + {static} open_graph3d()
}

class snake_game {
  + {static} open_snake()
}

' Quan hệ phụ thuộc (Dependency) từ Menu chính gọi đến các module chức năng
MainMenu ..> calculator : <<use>>
MainMenu ..> converter : <<use>>
MainMenu ..> graph : <<use>>
MainMenu ..> graph_3D : <<use>>
MainMenu ..> snake_game : <<use>>

note bottom of MainMenu
  The main Tkinter interface acts
  as a navigation tool, guiding
  users to the corresponding
  functions via buttons.
end note

note "These classes represent independent functional modules." as N1
calculator .. N1
converter .. N1
graph .. N1
graph_3D .. N1
snake_game .. N1

@enduml
